Makes 1 big jar
/////
Prep:
  Slice:
          3* zucchinis
          2* shallots
          1* red chilli
  Salt generously and leave for a couple of hours to draw moisture out
  Drain the water
  Pat dry
  Put into a jar along with:
        A handful of roughly chopped dill
/////
Vinegar:
  Heat in a pan:
        200 ml apple cider vinegar
        200 ml white wine vinegar
        1/3 cup raw sugar
  Bring to boil and stir so that sugar is all dissolved
/////
  Pour vinegar into jar, seal it, let it cool, then refrigerate
Pickles are good after 1 day and up to 1 week
